1
00:00:10,860 --> 00:00:12,780
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you♪

2
00:00:12,820 --> 00:00:14,740
♪I added a few more strokes♪

3
00:00:14,740 --> 00:00:17,380
♪To the ending♪

4
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:21,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

5
00:00:21,860 --> 00:00:24,140
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

6
00:00:24,300 --> 00:00:28,220
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

7
00:00:28,340 --> 00:00:31,020
♪Yet, you didn't show up♪

8
00:00:31,140 --> 00:00:33,140
♪This love is full of regrets♪

9
00:00:33,300 --> 00:00:37,420
♪You are but a dream
in this fleeting life♪

10
00:00:40,260 --> 00:00:41,260
[Part For Ever]

11
00:00:41,260 --> 00:00:42,000
[Adapted from the novel by Jing Mo,]

12
00:00:42,000 --> 00:00:42,900
[My Lord,
Madam Doesn't Want to See You Again]

13
00:00:42,900 --> 00:00:44,780
[Episode 2]

14
00:00:54,780 --> 00:00:57,050
Ling, I had another nightmare.

15
00:01:03,780 --> 00:01:05,180
Dreams are caused by thoughts.

16
00:01:05,460 --> 00:01:06,100
You shouldn't take it to heart.

17
00:01:06,900 --> 00:01:07,770
Ling,

18
00:01:07,970 --> 00:01:10,020
I dreamed they were trying
to harm you again.

19
00:01:12,900 --> 00:01:13,370
Let me go!

20
00:01:13,370 --> 00:01:13,920
Trying to escape, huh?

21
00:01:13,920 --> 00:01:14,580
Let me go!

22
00:01:14,580 --> 00:01:15,760
I'll break your leg
if you try to escape again!

23
00:01:15,760 --> 00:01:16,900
You better behave!

24
00:01:17,310 --> 00:01:18,390
My eyes...

25
00:01:18,750 --> 00:01:19,720
My eyes...

26
00:01:20,750 --> 00:01:21,720
My eyes.

27
00:01:27,310 --> 00:01:29,360
Don't be scared, I'll help you.

28
00:01:35,940 --> 00:01:42,460
♪The lonely goose cries in sorrow♪

29
00:01:44,280 --> 00:01:46,030
Yue, thank you

30
00:01:46,920 --> 00:01:47,750
for helping me back then.

31
00:01:52,360 --> 00:01:53,230
Ling,

32
00:01:54,110 --> 00:01:56,360
my heart aches at the thought
of you almost being sold off

33
00:01:56,750 --> 00:01:58,230
by the villains.

34
00:01:59,110 --> 00:02:00,310
If the former City Lord

35
00:02:00,310 --> 00:02:01,560
hadn't ruined your family,

36
00:02:02,150 --> 00:02:03,640
you wouldn't have fallen to this.

37
00:02:04,230 --> 00:02:05,080
Now,

38
00:02:05,080 --> 00:02:07,080
you've finally avenged your family.

39
00:02:07,080 --> 00:02:09,040
But you have to marry
the enemy's daughter.

40
00:02:11,160 --> 00:02:12,110
Ling,

41
00:02:12,880 --> 00:02:15,110
I only wish you'd stop
making yourself miserable.

42
00:02:15,940 --> 00:02:20,260
♪Even good times are spent in vain♪

43
00:02:24,360 --> 00:02:26,550
I must use her head

44
00:02:27,710 --> 00:02:30,830
to commemorate
the Ling family's tragedy.

45
00:02:56,600 --> 00:02:58,040
I have to think of a way
to rescue Mr. Zhao

46
00:02:58,510 --> 00:03:00,230
before he arrives.

47
00:03:10,270 --> 00:03:10,880
Open the door!

48
00:03:11,830 --> 00:03:12,670
Open this door now!

49
00:03:12,830 --> 00:03:13,990
Let me out!

50
00:04:08,830 --> 00:04:09,640
Pardon me.

51
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:18,840
It's you.

52
00:04:25,600 --> 00:04:26,400
What?

53
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:30,800
I mean, you're Miss Wan'er, right?

54
00:04:31,670 --> 00:04:32,480
Yes.

55
00:04:32,870 --> 00:04:33,750
You are...

56
00:04:35,960 --> 00:04:37,160
I'm Niyue,

57
00:04:37,160 --> 00:04:38,110
a female physician.

58
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:39,840
I'm especially here to help you.

59
00:04:45,160 --> 00:04:46,070
Miss Wan'er,

60
00:04:46,210 --> 00:04:48,550
I know Ling is using Commander Zhao
to make you comply.

61
00:04:49,480 --> 00:04:50,820
Without the City Lord's seal,

62
00:04:50,960 --> 00:04:53,120
it's hard to rescue Commander Zhao.

63
00:04:53,480 --> 00:04:55,110
I grew up with Ling,

64
00:04:55,480 --> 00:04:57,480
so the prison guards will listen to me.

65
00:04:58,230 --> 00:04:59,230
Why are you helping me?

66
00:05:00,430 --> 00:05:01,430
To be honest,

67
00:05:01,800 --> 00:05:03,400
Ling and I love each other.

68
00:05:03,870 --> 00:05:05,040
Helping you

69
00:05:05,040 --> 00:05:06,280
is helping myself too.

70
00:05:09,360 --> 00:05:09,870
No need.

71
00:05:10,670 --> 00:05:12,070
I don't need to trouble you
with my affairs.

72
00:05:43,400 --> 00:05:44,110
Are you all right?

73
00:05:44,990 --> 00:05:46,040
I'm fine, Ling.

74
00:05:47,520 --> 00:05:49,040
Please don't blame Miss Wan'er.

75
00:05:49,400 --> 00:05:51,070
It was my fault for tripping.

76
00:05:51,520 --> 00:05:53,430
Miss Wan'er didn't push me on purpose.

77
00:06:02,070 --> 00:06:03,430
You're all birds of a feather.

78
00:06:07,670 --> 00:06:09,750
Go back to your room and get some rest.

79
00:06:37,840 --> 00:06:38,600
Keep going.

80
00:06:39,630 --> 00:06:41,190
You must be dreaming

81
00:06:41,600 --> 00:06:42,480
if you want me to comply obediently.

82
00:06:47,040 --> 00:06:47,840
Mr. Wang.

83
00:06:57,040 --> 00:06:57,630
Your Lordship,

84
00:06:58,550 --> 00:07:00,310
I've caught the carrier pigeon

85
00:07:00,720 --> 00:07:01,630
that Her Ladyship sent out.

86
00:07:03,310 --> 00:07:05,110
How about I read its content?

87
00:07:07,840 --> 00:07:08,600
Wang Zhen,

88
00:07:09,230 --> 00:07:10,400
I can't believe you defected!

89
00:07:11,110 --> 00:07:13,160
"Even a fine bird chooses a good tree
to nest."

90
00:07:13,400 --> 00:07:14,720
Let alone me.

91
00:07:24,800 --> 00:07:25,630
"Jing Tian,

92
00:07:26,230 --> 00:07:27,670
[Wan'er]
there was a hostile takeover.

93
00:07:28,630 --> 00:07:29,430
Come quickly."

94
00:07:33,230 --> 00:07:34,400
Your Lordship, this is bad news.

95
00:07:35,040 --> 00:07:35,630
Her Ladyship tried

96
00:07:35,630 --> 00:07:37,550
to inform her lover about the situation.

97
00:07:38,960 --> 00:07:41,480
Lover?

98
00:07:43,920 --> 00:07:45,720
Your Lordship, you are unaware.

99
00:07:46,110 --> 00:07:47,990
She and Jing Tian,
the son of the City Lord of Baiyu City,

100
00:07:47,990 --> 00:07:49,070
have long been engaged.

101
00:07:50,110 --> 00:07:51,280
They are childhood sweethearts

102
00:07:51,480 --> 00:07:52,720
and deeply in love with each other.

103
00:07:53,230 --> 00:07:54,840
I cannot accept

104
00:07:55,870 --> 00:07:57,450
a woman with two husbands.

105
00:07:57,750 --> 00:07:59,750
I don't want to be your wife.

106
00:08:00,840 --> 00:08:02,280
You might as well let me go now.

107
00:08:02,890 --> 00:08:04,550
Otherwise, Jing Tian will not spare you.

108
00:08:06,200 --> 00:08:07,360
I can't wait

109
00:08:07,360 --> 00:08:09,720
for your childhood sweetheart
to send himself to his death.

110
00:08:10,040 --> 00:08:10,720
You...

111
00:08:17,600 --> 00:08:19,720
Ling Xiao, listen.

112
00:08:20,160 --> 00:08:21,960
Even if you take the position
of the City Lord,

113
00:08:23,060 --> 00:08:24,960
everything in the City Lord's Mansion

114
00:08:25,600 --> 00:08:27,190
will always belong to the Su family.

115
00:08:34,070 --> 00:08:35,040
Is that so?

116
00:08:52,240 --> 00:08:53,520
Let me go!

117
00:08:54,400 --> 00:08:55,240
Let me go!

118
00:09:04,640 --> 00:09:06,040
Put me down!

119
00:09:11,140 --> 00:09:17,100
♪I spread out paper and pen,
writing a quatrain♪

120
00:09:17,800 --> 00:09:19,000
What are you doing?

121
00:09:19,000 --> 00:09:20,640
Don't touch my father's things!

122
00:09:22,430 --> 00:09:23,240
Calm down.

123
00:09:25,000 --> 00:09:26,710
The best is yet to come.

124
00:09:34,710 --> 00:09:36,470
No!

125
00:09:37,700 --> 00:09:43,380
♪This life is also tumultuous,
what use is there to confide in?♪

126
00:09:45,350 --> 00:09:47,000
No!

127
00:09:49,240 --> 00:09:51,000
My father is already gone.

128
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:54,190
These things are my only solace.

129
00:09:54,520 --> 00:09:56,120
Don't destroy them.

130
00:09:57,550 --> 00:09:58,760
Do you see clearly now?

131
00:09:59,310 --> 00:10:02,550
Whose territory
the City Lord's Mansion is?

132
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:06,540
♪To the ending♪

133
00:10:06,740 --> 00:10:10,580
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪

134
00:10:10,820 --> 00:10:13,220
♪Leaving only memories behind♪

135
00:10:13,340 --> 00:10:17,140
♪The wind blows from a long distance♪

136
00:10:17,140 --> 00:10:19,060
[Su]

137
00:10:20,260 --> 00:10:25,700
♪This love is full of regrets.
You're a dream in this fleeting life♪

138
00:10:26,180 --> 00:10:29,180
[Ling]

139
00:10:40,350 --> 00:10:41,160
Ling Xiao,

140
00:10:41,590 --> 00:10:42,800
why are you doing this?

141
00:10:43,120 --> 00:10:44,520
Everything about your father

142
00:10:45,240 --> 00:10:47,000
is filthy, disgusting, and stinky.

143
00:10:47,430 --> 00:10:49,160
If you have problems,
you can vent it on me.

144
00:10:49,240 --> 00:10:50,550
Don't insult my father.

145
00:10:52,800 --> 00:10:53,710
Do you think

146
00:10:54,760 --> 00:10:56,070
you can escape?

147
00:10:56,940 --> 00:11:00,500
♪I foolishly think♪

148
00:11:00,700 --> 00:11:04,140
♪Unable to sleep,
intoxicated by the fragrance of books♪

149
00:11:04,310 --> 00:11:05,950
You can only leave

150
00:11:07,240 --> 00:11:08,640
when you wash away

151
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,430
this stench on you.

152
00:11:10,430 --> 00:11:11,240
Ling Xiao,

153
00:11:11,760 --> 00:11:12,830
your ruthless ambition

154
00:11:12,830 --> 00:11:14,590
of committing rebellion goes
against the heavens.

155
00:11:14,590 --> 00:11:15,950
You will definitely face retribution.

156
00:11:25,830 --> 00:11:27,950
My patience has a limit.

157
00:11:30,670 --> 00:11:32,760
You should know the consequences
of going against me.

158
00:11:34,470 --> 00:11:35,280
Now, wash.

159
00:12:05,660 --> 00:12:12,300
♪Rain falls in the courtyard,
stirring up idle worries♪

160
00:12:12,380 --> 00:12:18,340
♪I spread out paper and pen,
writing a quatrain♪

161
00:12:18,820 --> 00:12:25,580
♪I think of you again as I write down
the past memories♪

162
00:12:25,700 --> 00:12:31,620
♪Who did I share my emotions
during those years?♪

163
00:12:32,100 --> 00:12:38,820
♪Threads of emotions linger,
deeply immersed in your features♪

164
00:12:39,020 --> 00:12:44,620
♪This life is also tumultuous,
what use is there to confide in?♪

165
00:12:44,740 --> 00:12:51,900
♪The clear wind points to the love
and separation, so poignant♪

166
00:12:52,020 --> 00:12:58,580
♪As if you haven't left yet♪

167
00:13:01,340 --> 00:13:05,100
♪The wind blows, but I don't see you.
I added a few more strokes♪

168
00:13:05,260 --> 00:13:07,900
♪To the ending♪

169
00:13:07,980 --> 00:13:11,500
♪With the flowers falling
and the time passing♪
